WEBVTT

00:13.520 --> 00:14.320
Come in

00:21.360 --> 00:23.960
This old minister heard Your Majesty was hit by an arrow

00:24.320 --> 00:25.640
Was greatly alarmed

00:26.360 --> 00:28.200
Now seeing Your Majesty safe

00:28.480 --> 00:30.560
This old minister is at ease

00:34.360 --> 00:35.840
This is Li Dingyuan's memorial

00:39.480 --> 00:40.240
Your Majesty

00:40.560 --> 00:42.240
Your servant has verified everything

00:42.800 --> 00:44.000
The Xie family colluded with factions

00:44.840 --> 00:46.640
Embezzled state taxes at every level

00:47.280 --> 00:48.160
Originally two hundred taels of silver

00:48.760 --> 00:49.680
When it reached the court

00:49.960 --> 00:51.160
Only one hundred taels remained

00:55.160 --> 00:56.840
Take a look

01:02.440 --> 01:04.560
You and I have been ruler and minister

01:05.800 --> 01:08.560
Everyone has their own account in their heart

01:09.880 --> 01:12.000
Others may not remember this bond

01:12.640 --> 01:13.480
But I

01:15.440 --> 01:16.960
Cannot forget

01:17.920 --> 01:19.040
These years

01:19.840 --> 01:20.840
What you've done

01:21.840 --> 01:24.280
You and I both understand in our hearts

01:25.840 --> 01:26.720
False accusation

01:27.160 --> 01:28.680
These are all false accusations

01:31.640 --> 01:32.360
Your Majesty

01:32.520 --> 01:36.840
This old minister has followed Your Majesty since the second year of Yuankang

01:37.400 --> 01:41.360
This old minister has never had disloyal thoughts toward Your Majesty

01:48.160 --> 01:48.800
I

01:52.360 --> 01:54.680
Have little time left

01:59.880 --> 02:01.560
While I am here

02:03.480 --> 02:05.280
I can still tolerate you

02:06.920 --> 02:08.120
When I'm gone

02:09.680 --> 02:10.760
Xuan Kingdom

02:11.680 --> 02:13.240
Cannot tolerate you

02:21.360 --> 02:22.040
Your servant

02:23.920 --> 02:25.840
Your servant is guilty

02:27.720 --> 02:30.840
Your servant is ashamed before Your Majesty
